      * GET MACHINE USAGE
     C                     EXSR #MCN
      * GETKANBAN QTY
     C                     EXSR #RQTY
      *
     C                     ADD  1         RRN2
     C                     WRITESFL02
     C                     ADD  1         X
      *
     C**         X         IFEQ 17
     C**                   LEAVE
     C**                   ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
